ActInternational Boundary Waters Treaty Act
PrecisReappointment of FRANCIS HENRY LICKERS of Cornwall, Ontario, as a Commissioner of the International Joint Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending on December 31, 2023, or until such time as a new commissioner is appointed, whichever comes first, effective May 9, 2023.
